ExifTool is a highly customizable Perl script and module for reading,
writing and editing meta information in a wide variety of files.

ExifTool supports many different metadata formats including EXIF, GPS, IPTC,
XMP, JFIF, GeoTIFF, ICC Profile, Photoshop IRB, FlashPix, AFCP and ID3,
Lyrics3, as well as the maker notes of many digital cameras by Canon, Casio,
DJI, FLIR, FujiFilm, GE, GoPro, HP, JVC/Victor, Kodak, Leaf,
Minolta/Konica-Minolta, Motorola, Nikon, Nintendo, Olympus/Epson,
Panasonic/Leica, Pentax/Asahi, Phase One, Reconyx, Ricoh, Samsung, Sanyo,
Sigma/Foveon and Sony.
